  "dialogue": {
    "1": {
      "id": "1",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*You and Gale find it hard enough to tolerate each other as it is. It seems unlikely that a revelation like this will do anything but widen the gulf between you.*",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "Approval_AtLeast_0_For_Sp2 = False"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "16",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "5": {
          "id": "5",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Trust in Gale. Tell him the truth about yourself. Ask for acceptance.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "Approval_AtLeast_20_For_Sp2"
          ],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "16",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "0": {
              "id": "0",
              "speaker": "",
              "text": "True",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "16",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "rollresult",
              "children": {
                "17": {
                  "id": "17",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "I knew you had some dark secret to hide, but a vampire spawn? It wouldn't have been my first guess, I'll put it that way.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [
                    "ORI_Astarion_Knows_Vampireness"
                  ],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "16",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {}
                }
              }
            },
            "23": {
              "id": "23",
              "speaker": "",
              "text": "False",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "9",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "rollresult",
              "children": {
                "10": {
                  "id": "10",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "I'd have appreciated your honesty a lot more had it been offered prior to us setting off on this adventure together.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [
                    "ORI_Astarion_Knows_Vampireness",
                    "45ccb032-318b-292d-b2e5-cd93d3a87d16_AstarionVampreConfessionNegativeReaction"
                  ],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "9",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "11": {
                      "id": "11",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "My neck's puncture-free, I've not experienced any overwhelming desire to exsanguinate my nearest and dearest... I can only conclude there's no harm done.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Neutral, running through a checklist - might have reacted positively or negatively prior to this",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "9",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "16": {
                          "id": "16",
                          "speaker": "Gale",
                          "text": "But what does this revelation of yours mean for us going forward?",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "9",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "26": {
                              "id": "26",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "It doesn't change anything. I'm still the same loveable rogue I always was.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "9",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "4": {
                                  "id": "4",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "Debatable. But our common goals remain common, so I see no point in depriving each other of an ally.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [
                                    "45ccb032-318b-292d-b2e5-cd93d3a87d16_AstarionVampreConfessionNegativeReaction"
                                  ],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "9",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                },
                                "28": {
                                  "id": "28",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "Now with added bite.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: Sense of an eyebrow raised at the idea this hasn't changed anything",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "9",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "21": {
                              "id": "21",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "It makes the removal of my tadpole more complicated. That's the reason I can walk in the sun.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "9",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "3": {
                                  "id": "3",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "And gods forbid it should be you who's kept in the dark.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: Sarcastic - Gale's been kept in the dar (in the lied to sense) by Astarion until now",
                                  "checkflags": [
                                    "45ccb032-318b-292d-b2e5-cd93d3a87d16_AstarionVampreConfessionNegativeReaction"
                                  ],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "9",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "9": {
                                      "id": "9",
                                      "speaker": "Gale",
                                      "text": "For now, let's consider that particular matter settled. Was that the only thing on your mind?",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
                                "18": {
                                  "id": "18",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "Is that so? Well let's hope that continues to be the case. There's no guarantee our cure will be found lurking in the darkness, after all.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "9",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "25": {
                              "id": "25",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I have a Master. He may come looking for me...",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "9",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "8": {
                                  "id": "8",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "A vampire and a fugitive? You've got everything going for you, haven't you?",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: Sarcastic, qith a sigh - at this point, unfazed by anything",
                                  "checkflags": [
                                    "45ccb032-318b-292d-b2e5-cd93d3a87d16_AstarionVampreConfessionNegativeReaction"
                                  ],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "9",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                },
                                "7": {
                                  "id": "7",
                                  "speaker": "Gale",
                                  "text": "And if he does, he'll not find you alone.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: Promising to stand by Astarion if his master pursues him",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "9",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "12": {
          "id": "12",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Be blunt. Tell Gale the truth. Hope your honesty is enough.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "Approval_AtLeast_0_For_Sp2 = False"
